### =========================================================
### HEALTH
### =========================================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics


### =========================================================
### AUTH
### =========================================================

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alpesh",
  "email": "alpesh@1example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}


### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alpesh@1example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}


### Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### =========================================================
### FILES
### =========================================================

### Get Storage Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/storage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### List Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/files
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get File By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/FILE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Delete File
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/FILE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get File Versions
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/FILE_ID_HERE/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Create Share Link
POST {{baseUrl}}/files/FILE_ID_HERE/share
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expiresInHours": 24
}


### Resolve Share Link
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/shared/SHARE_TOKEN_HERE


### =========================================================
### UPLOADS
### =========================================================

### Single File Upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./test.txt
--boundary--


### Upload Same File Again (Dedup Test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./test.txt
--boundary--


### =========================================================
### MULTIPART
### =========================================================

### Multipart Init
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/multipart/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "large-video.mp4",
  "mimeType": "video/mp4",
  "totalSize": 50000000,
  "chunkCount": 5
}


### Multipart Complete
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/multipart/FILE_ID_HERE/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parts": [
    {
      "partNumber": 1,
      "etag": "etag-1"
    }
  ]
}


### =========================================================
### INVALID TOKEN TEST
### =========================================================

### Invalid JWT
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token


